headline.main: Astronauts Hope for '61 Flight; All Seven Are Eager to Make the First Trip Into Space

results.snippet: CAPE CANAVERAL, Fla., Sept. 16 (AP) -- America's seven Mercury astronauts are ready, eager and confident as the day approaches for one of them to spin into space. Each of them wants to be first.

results.lead_paragraph: THE name of the first astronaut will surely be long remembered in the records of history. But others will follow. headline.main: Khrushchev Says Soviet Is Ready To Put an Astronaut Into Space; SOVIET IS 'READY' FOR MAN IN SPACE
